{
  "stem": "22447.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then I get called-- you're wanted in the office.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What is it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You'll find out quick enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Went back into the office.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The colonel of the camp was there, the camp-- like British officer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Are you the soldier that canceled my pass?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They want Irma Grese to go to the cellar?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He says, if I give a pass, I'm lieutenant colonel of this camp, camp commandant.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Who are you to cancel that authority?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I said, so I  said, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the-- I thought she's, she's not, she's not entitled to it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He says, if I give a pass, I don't expect anybody to cancel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "What, what authority have you got to cancel it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So with that, the sergeant chimes in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Oh, and he threw his identity card down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He says, that's my authority, lieutenant colonel, I think his name was [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Byrd ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I've been all my lifetime in the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that's my-- and he threw it down like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he said, that's my authority.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So the sergeant said, that's your authority?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Well, I'll trump it here with my authority.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He threw down a warrant card.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I had a warrant card as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And every policeman, military or civilian, carries what was known as a warrant card, which gives you the authority to do whatever you think in the line of duty.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know who signs the civilian, maybe the commissioner for police, or maybe [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I threw that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I says, that's my authority.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I threw down my warrant card.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Apparently, he hadn't seen it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he read it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the sergeant said, well, if you just sign this form, I'll forward it on to the provost marshal.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
